data.title: King's Birthday 2024 Honours List
data.meta_description: Almost 500 people are recognised in the general division of the King's Birthday Honours List, with the youngest...
data.text:
Governor-General David Hurley has released the King's Birthday Honours List, saluting many Aussies. (Lukas Coch/AAP PHOTOS)

The Governor-General is pleased to announce the following appointments and awards:
